{"tid":1990763,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Hi PTCG online & 中日美版實體卡谷","createTime":"2020-04-27T03:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T12:39:20.000Z","uid":116069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0161d727463c783501cb0fa30f9d2a233d96ab9","tid":1990763,"uid":116069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HnDtphGFChXGdqJGwGsKQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHnDtphGFChXGdqJGwGsKQw&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4IaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=506a6891\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HnDtphGFChXGdqJGwGsKQw</a><br />\n<br />\nHi 🖐🏻☝🏻everyone <br />\n依個係Pokemon card game嘅手谷都開左有一年多喇<br />\n儲就儲左一堆CD ROM有時有人放下卡咁<br />\n<br />\n當初開谷最想係有多d砌deck嘅交流<br />\n希望係非meta deck都搵到樂趣<br />\n強度 vs 悶度 vs 銀彈$ 取得平衡<br />\n<br />\n自己就本地比賽同日本比賽都會睇下<br />\n日本比賽吸引在個班精英會試新卡<br />\n砌一個新環境出嚟<br />\n香港主流就而家環境最強係邊幾副<br />\n自己唔砌輸左咪傻仔<br />\n好想香港都會有班人肯諗肯試多啲新deck<br />\n而唔係大部份人只砌幾副最meta<br />\n<br />\n可以係谷內trade卡 係自由交易<br />\n但絕對唔可以有欺騙成份!!! (有發現即踢)<br />\n<br />\n🚩基本谷規：<br />\n1. 互相尊重 有問題請有禮貌地問<br />\n2. 唔好亂用粗言穢語<br />\n3. 唔好映射/人生攻擊<br />\n4. 嚴禁保險/美容/健康產品推銷 (有發現即踢)<br />\n5. 勿煩膠地溝仔溝女<br />\n<br />\n觀迎入嚟傾下deck 同放卡<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HnDtphGFChXGdqJGwGsKQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHnDtphGFChXGdqJGwGsKQw&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4IaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=506a6891\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HnDtphGFChXGdqJGwGsKQw</a>"},{"pid":"acbcf6ce9a9deb00821ad6ed673003d4a5f93e5b","tid":1990763,"uid":116069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"884e19fa18ee3f0568c6b3adbc66db9f5b556425","tid":1990763,"uid":116069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"就收工 推推post"},{"pid":"4ffff2f8153cf463ecec4bf2797320105adb932d","tid":1990763,"uid":223523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci